title: Corsair Abidjan Service cancelled from late-October 2015
text:
Corsair Abidjan Service cancelled from late-October 2015   
Sep 23, 2015 eTN   
Beginning of Winter 2015/2016 Corsair is cancelling service to Cote d’Ivoire, as the airline closed reservation for Paris Orly – Abidjan route. The airline originally planned to operate three weekly flights with A330, on/after 25 October 2015. 
Previously planned schedule as follow. SS984 ORY1515 – 2045ABJ 330 257 SS985 ABJ2250 – 0620+1ORY 330 257
